[Previous reports of Ebola hemorrhagic fever in Kenya have not been
confirmed by laboratory investigation. There is a suggestion in the present
report that the patient may have undergone some rather aggressive therapy,
which may in part have been responsible for the deterioration in her
condition. - Mod.CP
